master.title: Sex Machine

master.notes: On March 21st 1987 Prince held a unannounced 65-minute rehearsal for his 'Sign O' The Times' tour at 'First Avenue' in Minneapolis. The sequence was performed as follows: Housequake • Girls And Boys • Slow Love • Hot Thing • Now's The Time • Strange Relationship • Forever In My Life • Kiss • It's Gonna Be A Beautiful Night (incorporating the horn riff from Madhouse's 'Six' and Duke Ellington's 'Take The A-Train') •This master-release groups together unofficial releases of the audiotrack from the never released footage.In 2004 'Strange Relationship' was released on [l621914] to download.
